    ScenarioOutputImpl
    public interface ScenarioOutput
extends org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject
    A representation of the model object 'Scenario Output'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Scenario
    • Operationsignature
    • Operationinterface
    • Connector
    • Decision
    • Policy IDs
